        "subject": "LU-19856 build: remove RHEL7isms from lustre.spec.in",
        "message": "LU-19856 build: remove RHEL7isms from lustre.spec.in\n\nRemove handling for RHEL7.x kernels from lustre.spec.in.  All new\ndistro's \"rpm\" handling understands \"Recommends\".\n\nUpdate the minimum kernel version to RHEL8, at least Linux 4.18.\n\nTest-Parameters: trivial\nSigned-off-by: Andreas Dilger <adilger@thelustrecollective.com>\nChange-Id: I8ffafc4997cb279a9c5ff834aea2d6a1c10a33a8\nReviewed-on: https://review.whamcloud.com/c/fs/lustre-release/+/65226\nTested-by: jenkins <devops@whamcloud.com>\nTested-by: Maloo <maloo@whamcloud.com>\nReviewed-by: Jian Yu <yujian@whamcloud.com>\nReviewed-by: Oleg Drokin <green@whamcloud.com>\nReviewed-by: James Simmons <jsimmons@infradead.org>\n"
